      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">Gallium occurs in minute quantities in the Earth's crust, </text>
   </par>
   <par align="l" li="0" ri="0" iln="0">
      <text fn="Arial" fh="15" fc="16777215" fa="1" charset="238">making up just </text>
